{
  "stem": "3804.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would say after war-- after high technical school, and then I went to the army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because I was known in the high technical school as good in technology and I like locks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I like safes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I liked explosives and all this-- in the Haganah, I already studied explosives, you know-- how do you say-- anti-explosives to be-- to protect yourself from explosives, and also, how to make explosives, how to make mines and all these kind of-- how do you--",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Booby traps and all these kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then I-- there was a problem there, a technical problem that they had.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When they went to the school or back to the Technion that I studied already, didn't finish as an engineer-- they said, he can solve you the problem-- the secret service-- and he can solve your problem.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was something-- you know, through the, through the war was something-- say, it was mined, and also couldn't open it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I helped it-- helped to take away the mine, you know, the booby trap, and open it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they said, why shouldn't you continue to work with us?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never thought about that I'm going to be the secret service.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my mother, she wants me to be an engineer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I, I went to the high technical school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said it's all-- it looks like that she helped me to be in the secret service, in a way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But you couldn't tell anyone?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't tell her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you don't tell your Jewish mother that you went to the secret service.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After what all happened to our family, there's no way you can tell her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because she always would be very worried.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
